graph TD
    A[Start Task] --> B{Task Objective Defined}
    B --> C[Plan Agent: Generate Plan]
    C --> D[Implement Agent: Write/Modify Code]
    D --> E[Test Agent: Execute Tests]
    E -- Tests Pass --> F[Review Agent: Code Review]
    E -- Tests Fail --> G[Debug Agent: Analyze Failures]
    G --> D
    F --> H[Commit Agent: Commit Changes]
    H --> I[Reflect Agent: Analyze Iteration]
    I -- Improvements Needed --> C
    I -- Task Complete --> J[End Task]
